  "text": "Goop founder Gwyneth Paltrow has teamed up with CB2 to create another instantly classic collaboration â€“ and we can’t get enough of it. The enchanting Leggero Plug-In Wall Sconce beautifully captures everything we love about this collection. It’s effortlessly elegant, it abounds with unexpected details, and it’s practical too! It offers the soft atmospheric lighting that only a sconce can provide, but without the complicated installation requirements. Just mount it, plug it in, and enjoy. This sconce is crafted from durable iron with a sophisticated champagne brass finish polished to a brilliant shine. A cotton/linen lampshade gently diffuses the lighting from the bulb within. It’s compatible with your choice of a 40W candelabra bulb or a 4W candelabra LED bulb. Even the cord features a high-end fabric finish for a clean appearance. Leggero sconces are a high ceiling’s best friend. While ordinary sconces can become visually overshadowed by a large room, these make a bold visual impact through their extended length. They offer the exaggerated proportions of a torchiere while remaining sleek and visually elegant. The decorative applications are endless. Use these sconces to flank a dramatic architectural element like a fireplace or let them serve as an interesting alternative to bedside lamps. They’d also excel in any accent placement, perhaps at the entryway or beside a writing desk. And if you decide to rearrange, the plug-and-play installation ensures you can easily move the sconces along with your furniture. Get it at CB2. Use to complement classic and contemporary decor themes alike â€“ the clean lines lean modern while the glamorous finishes could read timeless or traditional. Leggero is a highly versatile sconce both in terms of aesthetics and functionality, sure to become a favorite that will remain relevant through every renovation and redecoration project.",
