he lighting from the bulb within. It’s compatible with your choice of a 40W candelabra bulb or a 4W candelabra LED bulb. Even the cord features a high-end fabric finish for a clean appearance.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://sovrn.co/1oiwv3k\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener sponsored\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"904\" height=\"990\" src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/elegant-plug-in-wall-sconces-flanking-fireplace-unique-extra-long-decorative-lighting-for-high-ceilings.jpg\" alt=\"Two Leggero plug-in wall sconces flanking a fireplace\" srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/elegant-plug-in-wall-sconces-flanking-fireplace-unique-extra-long-decorative-lighting-for-high-ceilings.jpg 904w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/elegant-plug-in-wall-sconces-flanking-fireplace-unique-extra-long-decorative-lighting-for-high-ceilings-600x657.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/elegant-plug-in-wall-sconces-flanking-fireplace-unique-extra-long-decorative-lighting-for-high-ceilings-768x841.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 904px) 100vw, 904px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20904%20990\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/elegant-plug-in-wall-sconces-flanking-fireplace-unique-extra-long-decorative-lighting-for-high-ceilings.jpg 904w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/elegant-plug-in-wall-sconces-flanking-fireplace-unique-extra-long-decorative-lighting-for-high-ceilings-600x657.jpg 600w, https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/elegant-plug-in-wall-sconces-flanking-fireplace-unique-extra-long-decorative-lighting-for-high-ceilings-768x841.jpg 768w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.home-designing.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/el